      <p class="story-body reveal d2">Today, we curate 100+ trusted brands — O3+, WOW, Mamaearth, L'Oréal, and more — sourced directly from brands and authorised distributors. No fakes. No grey market. No compromise. Featured in the Economic Times, trusted by customers across India.</p>
